<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
    <title>Order - Turned In</title>
    <%- include("../../partials/head.ejs") %>
<body>
    <!-- Header -->
    <%- include("../../partials/header.ejs") %>
    <!--End Header-->

    <!--Banner-->
    <div class="w-100 bg-warning py-3 mb-5">
        <div class="text-center text-light">
            <span> Cek Turnitin 24 Jam </span>
        </div>
    </div>
<!--End Banner-->

</header>

    <!-- Main Section -->
     <main>
        <div class="container py-4">
            <!-- Card -->
            <div class="shadow p-3 mb-5 bg-body-tertiary rounded w-75 mx-auto">
                <span class="fw-bold mb-5">JASA TRANSLATE</span>
                <div class="shadow-sm p-3 mb-5 bg-body-tertiary rounded">
                    <div class="button-container">
                        <button type="button" class="btn btn-danger btn-sm float-md-end mx-1">Hapus Semua</button>
                        <button type="button" class="btn btn-primary btn-sm float-md-end mx-1">Unggah File</button>
                    </div>
                    <div class="container py-5">
                        <div class="text-center text-secondary fw-bold">
                            <h4>Jasa Translate</h4>
                            <span class="fw-semibold">TARIK FILE MU KESINI / KLIK AJA DISINI</span>
                            <p>.docx .pdf .pptx</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="d-flex justify-content-center">
                    <div class="container mt-1 py-2 p-5">
                        <div class="row">
                            <div class="col-12 col-xl-6 border-end">
                                <span class="fw-bold">1. Pilih translate ke bahasa apa yaa</span>
                                <div class="mb-3 py-2">
                                    <label for="exampleFormControlInput1" class="form-label text-normal">Translate ke Bahasa</label>
                                    <select class="form-select select-bar custom-select" aria-label="Default select example">
                                        <option selected>Pilih Bahasa</option>
                                        <option value="desc">Inggris</option>
                                        <option value="asc">Jepang</option>
                                        <option value="asc">Korea</option>
                                        <option value="asc">Thailand</option>
                                    </select>                                    
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="col-12 col-xl-6 py-0 p-4">
                                <span class="fw-bold">2. Isi Nomer Whatsapp kamu buat ngirim hasilnya</span>
                                <div class="row g-2 align-items-center">
                                    <div class="col-auto p-2 mb-3">
                                        <img src="https://www.techspot.com/images2/downloads/topdownload/2016/05/WhatsApp_Logo_1.png" width="20" height="20" alt="WhatsApp Logo">
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="col-auto">
                                        <input type="text" class="form-control" placeholder="62xxxxxxxxx" name="WhatsApp">
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="mb-3">
                                        <label for="exampleFormControlTextarea1" class="form-label">Catatan</label>
                                        <textarea class="form-control" id="exampleFormControlTextarea1" rows="2" placeholder="Contoh: Kata-katanya yang nyambung ya" name="catatan"></textarea>
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="text-dark fw-bold">
                                        <span>Jumlah: Rp 0</span>
                                        <span class="badge text-bg-secondary">Tawar</span>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="d-flex justify-content-center py-5">
                  <button type="button" class="btn btn-yellow text-light"> Order </button>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <!-- About -->
        <div class="w-100 bg-primary mt-5 mb-5">
            <div class="container">
              <div class="row">
                <div class="col-4">
                  <img src="/asset/pegang-buku.png" alt="" class="img-fluid img-about">
                </div>
                <div class="col-8 mt-5">
                  <div class="text-center fw-bold fz-25 text-light">
                    <span>Translate In itu apa sih?</span>
                  </div>
                  <div class="text-left fz-15 fw-semibold text-light ">
                    <p>Translate In adalah Translate In adalah layanan terjemahan file otomatis yang memudahkan Anda menerjemahkan berbagai jenis dokumen dengan akurasi tinggi. Terintegrasi dengan teknologi canggih, Translate In memastikan hasil terjemahan yang cepat dan efisien.</p>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <!--End About-->

          <!--Benefit-->
          <div class="container mt-5 mb-5 large-spacing">
            <div class="text-center">
                <h1 class="fw-bold fz-25 mt-4 mb-4">Biar apa pake Translate In?</h1>
                <p class="text-warning fw-bold fz-15 mt-4 mb-4">Biar dokumenmu bisa diubah bahasanya</p>
            </div>
        </div>
        <!--End Benefit-->
     </main>
     <!--End Main-->
     
     <!-- Footer -->
     <%- include("../../partials/footer.ejs") %>
     <!-- End Footer-->
  
    <!-- Bootstrap -->
    <%- include("../../partials/script.ejs") %>
</body>
</html>